TERRAFORM MODULE LICENSE

This Terraform module is designed to provision AWS infrastructure resources
including but not limited to:
- Amazon ECS Fargate clusters and services
- Application Load Balancers (ALB)
- Auto Scaling policies
- CloudWatch monitoring and alarms
- Security groups and IAM roles
- EFS file systems and S3 buckets

DISCLAIMER: This module creates AWS resources that may incur costs. Users are 
responsible for understanding AWS pricing, monitoring resource usage, and 
ensuring compliance with AWS terms of service and organizational security policies.

SECURITY: Users must review and validate all security configurations including
IAM policies, security groups, and network configurations before deploying to
production environments.

NO WARRANTY: This module is provided "as is" without warranty of any kind.
The authors are not responsible for any issues, security vulnerabilities, 
or costs that may arise from using this module.